name: Ky%27lee
content:
Ky'lee was a female Cathar ambassador residing on Carrick Station during the Galactic War between the Galactic Republic and the reconstituted Sith Empire.
Ambassador Ky'lee is a vendor added to Star Wars: The Old Republic: Knights of the Fallen Empire in Update 4.0, who sells rewards from the Grand Acquisitions Race event. It is also possible to obtain a decoration version of Ambassador Ky'lee, allowing people to place her in strongholds.
